assert.documentation: Log a message and stack trace to console if first argument is false.

count.documentation: Log the number of times this line has been called with the given label.

error.documentation: Outputs an error message. You may use string substitution and additional arguments with this method.

info.documentation: Informative logging information. You may use string substitution and additional arguments with this method.

log.documentation: For general output of logging information. You may use string substitution and additional arguments with this method.

time.documentation: Starts a timer with a name specified as an input parameter. Up to 10,000 simultaneous timers can run on a given page.

timeEnd.documentation: Stops the specified timer and logs the elapsed time in seconds since its start.

warn.documentation: Outputs a warning message. You may use string substitution and additional arguments with this method.
